nodes.text: Slum district G17 was a district on the planet Coruscant located in the underworld. It contained, among other things, the Spider Arms Hostel, several cabarets, at least two Noodle Bar diners, Chezdeze, Lauli Wahlo's noodle shop, a massage parlor, a gangster hangout, a gun market, and a bar in which Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker apprehended the Weequay criminal Car Affa.
